::Prowl::

Prowl sighs, looking down at the femm he loved, the femm he would always 
love. His arms hold her close to him, Prowl inhaling her scent. His eyes 
soften as he looks at her, hearing her question, and knowing that his plans 
would have to wait.

"Yeah. The Ark was attacked again. Its currently falling apart. Brooder and 
Arcangel have a plan for it, we need to meet them at the conference room."

He looks at Iron Raptor, his arms tightening around her. She was the bot he 
loved, the femm he wanted to be with all the time, but duty called.

"Shall we go, then?" he asks, looking at her with undying love in his optics.
